Step 2.3: When water reaches Sensor_Hi_2 = True -> Immediately stop filling (Pump_3 and Pump_4 stop). Wait for a manual discharge signal from the valves.
Step 2.4: When Valve_1 or Valve_2 is manually opened, the water level in Tank 2 decreases.
